title: Under President Donald J. Trump, Americans Are Getting Back To Work – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Economy & Jobs	

Issued on:
December 21, 2017
AMERICA’S ECONOMY IS FIRING ON ALL CYLINDERS: President Donald J. Trump has unleashed America’s economic growth engine and ushered in a new era of economic optimism.HARD AT WORK: The Department of Labor has implemented pro-growth programs, rolled back overreaching regulations, and taken action to support American workers.
